594
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:54,420
What do you want to eat then?

595
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,420
I'll pack it up and bring it to you.

596
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:57,570
Tell him to come himself!

597
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:58,900
