598
00:30:02,350 --> 00:30:03,010
Alright, go.

599
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,380
I'll wait in the car.

600
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,980
We'll be your delivery guys!

601
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:10,010
Hello, Uncle.

602
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,290
What do you want to eat?

603
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:21,330
Fei,

604
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,530
pack a few dishes to go.

605
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:03,980
Mentor!

606
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,700
So, your guess,

607
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:18,810
