608
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:21,220
Why would my mentor write his name?

609
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,290
Not yet.

610
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:29,180
But only

611
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,940
Mr. Xiang knows the truth.

612
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,090
No matter what,

613
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,330
