624
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:34,130
Please cooperate with the inspection.

625
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,570
Sir, your bag needs inspection.

626
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:44,420
Please come with us.

627
00:34:53,510 --> 00:34:54,530
What are you doing?

628
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:56,460
