629
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,530
We are not restricting you.

630
00:34:58,710 --> 00:35:00,210
You just need to wait here for a moment.

631
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,570
You want to check, right?

632
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,860
Fine.

633
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:08,940
Go ahead!

634
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:11,090
If you find nothing,

635
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:13,010
