636
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,690
You may not know this man,

637
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,260
but you should recognize

638
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,420
these two bags, right?

639
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:30,630
[China Customs]

640
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:31,260
[China Customs]
Shen,

641
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:34,380
[China Customs]
brief everyone

642
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,490
on the Liu Yang smuggling case.

643
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,050
Yes.

644
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,000
[Case: Smuggling Suspects and Network]

645
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,510
[Liu Yang Primary Suspect]

646
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,300
This time,

647
