650
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:48,650
We broke

651
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,940
an insider smuggling chain.

652
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:53,130
And unexpectedly,

653
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,210
starting from here,

654
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:56,170
we uncovered a highly organized

655
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,170
smuggling ring

656
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,490
