[35, Han. Handles one smuggling route.]
is only responsible for one route.

659
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:05,320
[Liu Yang Primary Suspect
35, Han. Handles one smuggling route.]

660
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,300
[Wang Suping 38 Han. One of the agents.]
Based on her confession

661
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:07,650
[Chen Yan, 28, Han. One of the agents.]
and the interrogation

662
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:09,780
of the arrested airport staff,

663
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,090
we can confirm

664
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:14,300
that Chen Yan and Wang Suping

665
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:17,300
are two more agents in the ring.

666
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:18,780
The three of them

667
00:36:19,230 --> 00:36:21,940
worked with insiders at the airport,

668
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:25,460
using concealment, disguise,
underreporting, misreporting,

669
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,860
and other methods

670
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:29,170
to evade customs supervision.

671
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:30,260
They

672
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:31,860
transported and carried

673
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:34,740
restricted and prohibited
imports and exports.

674
00:36:35,070 --> 00:36:36,090
Meanwhile,

675
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:37,090
these three people

676
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:39,210
posed as frequent travelers

677
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,130
[Tao Xi'e, Flight Attendant]
to get close to

678
00:36:40,510 --> 00:36:41,940
[Tao Xi'e, Flight Attendant]
flight attendants.

679
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,530
With high payouts,

680
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:47,530
they recruited
flight attendants into smuggling.

681
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,780
We're still

682
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:50,050
investigating this list.

683
00:36:50,050 --> 00:36:50,960
[Xiao Dabao, 33, Han. Actual leader.
MCN livestream smuggling; large-scale.]

684
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,050
This man is Xiao Dabao.

685
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:54,170
He's the upstream of Liu Yang's group,

686
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:57,130
also the real leader of the ring.

687
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:59,530
Their smuggled luxury goods

688
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:01,530
were sold

689
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:02,690
