691
00:37:04,150 --> 00:37:05,090
Huge profits involved.

692
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:06,980
[Huayan International Airport Staff]
Chief, I'm done.

693
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:09,460
Baggage handlers.

694
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:10,940
Cleaners.

695
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,130
Flight attendants.

696
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:15,690
[Huayan International Airport Staff]
These smugglers are everywhere.

697
00:37:15,690 --> 00:37:17,440
[Cleaners: Xu G., Meng T.
Baggage Staff: Jiang H., Xu Z., Liu J.]

698
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:19,210
GACC takes this very seriously.

699
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:21,260
The case in Binhai has been reported

700
00:37:21,590 --> 00:37:23,050
