702
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:26,920
[Cleaners: Xu G., Meng T.
Baggage Staff: Jiang H., Xu Z., Liu J.]

703
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:27,570
And,

704
00:37:27,570 --> 00:37:28,230
[Huayan International Airport Staff]

705
00:37:28,230 --> 00:37:28,900
this time,

706
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,740
Zhang Yu from Section I

707
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,740
caught

708
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:33,650
a small slip from the smugglers

709
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:36,090
