714
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:48,980
Comrades,

715
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,000
[Cleaners: Xu G., Meng T.
Baggage Staff: Jiang H., Xu Z., Liu J.]

716
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:50,610
next,

717
00:37:50,610 --> 00:37:51,320
[Huayan International Airport Staff]

718
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,460
