721
00:37:56,510 --> 00:37:58,090
A coordinated crackdown on both sides.

722
00:37:58,510 --> 00:37:59,690
All departments

723
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:00,820
are urged to act quickly

724
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,570
and carry out your work.

725
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:04,980
Confident?

726
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,340
Yes!

727
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,130
Dabao,

728
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:12,530
