731
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,860
I'm on the run!

732
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:18,210
Liu Yang and the others are arrested.

733
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,090
Customs is already
heading to the company.

734
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:21,380
I'll take care

735
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,860
