736
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,530
You pack up quickly.

737
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,130
I've arranged a boat tonight.

738
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:28,460
We'll head straight to Southeast Asia!

739
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,570
Go ahead, pack up.

740
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:30,940
I'm hanging up!

741
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:46,740
Dabao!

742
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:47,940
Li,

743
00:38:48,070 --> 00:38:49,820
