746
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,210
Yeah,

747
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:55,900
this money comes too slow.

748
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,090
Listen up,

749
00:38:57,110 --> 00:38:58,170
I've got a big job!

750
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:01,010
Just carrying goods across Customs.

751
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,130
As long as it makes money.

752
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:03,690
We're in, right?

753
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,860
Alright then,

754
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,860
let's work together,

755
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,010
big house,

756
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,490
