757
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:12,380
Honestly,

758
00:39:12,710 --> 00:39:13,980
their office

759
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:16,010
is impressive.

760
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,050
Don't worry.

761
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:21,980
Stick with me,

762
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,940
I'll get you one like that.

763
00:39:28,590 --> 00:39:29,260
Hello?

764
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:30,740
It's you.

765
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:32,420
Have you made up your mind?

766
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,380
I have.

767
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:37,460
Sa Ziyi's turf… I want all of it.

768
00:39:37,630 --> 00:39:39,650
And I want all your resources, too.

769
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:40,460
Okay.

770
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,460
Wait.

771
00:39:43,030 --> 00:39:45,010
I can't just keep calling you 'hey'.

772
00:39:45,190 --> 00:39:46,610
What should I call you?

773
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,690
Just call me Mr. E.

774
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:52,690
What do you think?

775
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:54,570
Huge!

776
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:55,900
Li,

777
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,570
nice place!

778
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:01,740
When do I get a place like that?

779
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,210
Look,

780
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:03,380
