784
00:40:46,230 --> 00:40:46,780
Hello, Dabao.

785
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,170
I've decided.

786
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:49,900
I'm not leaving yet.

787
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:52,820
Mr. E did this to me,

788
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,380
