789
00:40:55,670 --> 00:40:56,650
Don't talk me out of it.

790
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,980
Hide out for a few days.

791
00:40:59,110 --> 00:40:59,860
Wait for my call.

792
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:02,820
I'll be fine.

793
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:04,980
Liu Yang doesn't know me.

794
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:06,740
I've still got a few days.

795
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:08,090
Head over and wait.

796
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:10,170
If I can't find him,

797
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,170
I'll leave with you.

798
00:41:11,190 --> 00:41:11,740
Alright?

799
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:13,570
That's it.

800
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,130
Hello, Long Shuo.

801
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:32,420
It's Du Li.

802
00:42:04,590 --> 00:42:05,940
So this is your home with her?

803
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:07,130
Surprised, right?

804
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,820
Yeah, surprised.

805
00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:10,940
When I saw your office,

806
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,210
I thought you'd

807
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,740
live somewhere very luxurious.

808
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,210
She wanted to move.

809
00:42:15,710 --> 00:42:16,340
I didn't agree.

810
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,650
We lived here from the start.

811
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,300
Sit anywhere.

812
00:42:26,550 --> 00:42:27,340
Du Li,

813
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,420
I kind of respect you.

814
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:32,300
At this point,

815
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:33,740
you're still calm.

816
00:42:34,110 --> 00:42:36,050
Since I got into smuggling,

817
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,460
I've been ready

818
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,380
for this day.

819
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:39,650
I accept

820
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:40,420
being arrested.

821
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,130
But a stab

822
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,650
in the back,

823
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,380
I can't take that.

824
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:47,460
Are you sure

825
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:49,260
